File:

```
metadata.json
```

Example:

```json
{
    "run_time":
        "2026-07-21T15:34:39",

    "input_bundle":
        "sample_bundle.tgz",

    "agent":
        "RootCauseAnalysisAgent",

    "version":
        "0.1.0"
}
```

---

# Step 5: RCA Report

File:

```
report.json
```

Example:

```json
{
    "title":
        "Root Cause Analysis Report",

    "root_causes":
    [
        {
            "category":
                "ETHERNET_FAILURE",

            "confidence":
                92,

            "explanation":
                "Ethernet interface failure detected before downstream network failures",

            "evidence":
            [
                "kernel.log: NETDEV WATCHDOG timeout"
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

---

