---

# RCA Interpretation Example

Detected events:

```
10:00:01

eth0 link down


10:00:03

DHCP timeout


10:00:05

Internet unavailable
```

---

The Root Cause Engine determines:

```
Primary Failure:

ETHERNET_FAILURE


Secondary Symptoms:

DHCP_FAILURE

WAN_FAILURE
```

Reason:

```
Ethernet failure happened first.

Later failures are dependent symptoms.
```

